item.title: Prayer bpn13071 in Hiri Motu
item.description: Lohiabada e! Oi itaia, aiemai imana ai abiaisi Oiemu lalokau bona hariharibada gubana dekenai. Vadaeni, Oiemu lalokau bona hariharibada amo aiemai imana Oi hahonua. Aiemai kerere Oi gwauatao bona aiemai tamadia bona sinadia edia kerere danu Oi gwauatao, bona ai ura gaudia Oi hamomokania Oiemu hariharibada ena davara badana dekena amo. Aiemai lalokaku Tauna e! Oiemu dala dekenai ai karaia gaukaradia ibounai Oi abidiadae. Oi be momokani Siahu Ibounai bona Ataiai Momokani dekenai Noho Diravana.
